code: /**  * {@inheritDoc}  * The {@code ObjectMapper} must be configured with a {@code CBORFactory} instance.  */ @Override public void setObjectMapper(ObjectMapper objectMapper) {     Assert.isInstanceOf(CBORFactory.class, objectMapper.getFactory(), "CBORFactory required").     super.setObjectMapper(objectMapper). }
